data.description: GREAT LOCATION! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath is ready for you to enjoy. Home is located on a well-kept street in South Ridge and close to major highways, shopping centers, hospital, and area attractions. Soaring two-story foyer flows into the Formal Dining Room and large Kitchen with eating area, family room and office/den round out the first floor features. Enjoy the large back yard from the spacious deck, perfect for entertaining. 2nd floor features 4 great sized bedrooms & full bath including the Primary Suite with a walk-in closet & private bathroom. The partially finished basement has potential for additional finished living space. Don't miss out to own this home! Schedule your appointment today!
